# 🎯 3-MODE SYSTEM ORCHESTRATOR

> **TL;DR:** This is the central binding rule that orchestrates the entire Strategic/Tactical/Operational 3-mode system.
> It manages:
> - Mode detection and switching
> - Todo/handoff system
> - Integration of all mode-specific behaviors

## 🚨 CRITICAL RULE: UNIFIED TODO/HANDOFF SYSTEM IS MANDATORY 🚨

The unified todo/handoff document (`memory/project/todo-handoff.md`) MUST be created and maintained as the single source of truth for all work contracts between modes. NO mode can operate without this document.

